==English==
===Adjective===
'''fallow'''

#(''of agricultural land'') plowed but left unseeded for more than one planting season
# [[inactive]]; [[undeveloped]]
# A pale [[red]] or [[yellow]], light [[brown]], [[dun]].

====Derived terms====
*[[fallow deer]]
*[[fallowness]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# (''uncountable'') ground ploughed and harrowed but left unseeded for one year
# (''uncountable'') uncultivated [[land]]
# an area of fallow land

